com.revature.caliber.intel

Interface ClassroomStatisticalAnalysisBean


  • public interface ClassroomStatisticalAnalysisBean
    Defines the various algorithms required by the Reporting Service. Handles the complexity of measuring grades and statistical analyses. All methods must return grades as a percentage (%) of total raw score.
    Author:
    Patrick Walsh
